TI AM335x SDK and Rootfs Build
================================

Build in a chroot on centos x86_64 step-by-step instructions:

  oe-sdk-build

Local build without using network:

  oe-local-build


Build in Schroot
==================

See schroot-conf examples.


Alternate chroot packages
===========================

  $ sudo yum --installroot=/chroot/devel groupinstall "minimal install"


To install for ifconfig and ping:

  $ sudo yum --installroot=/chroot/devel install net-tools iputils
